# SkyWeb Change Log


## DN-9.4.2 — Alert Overlay Polish and Indicator Chart Cleanup

- Defaulted chart alert overlays to threshold-only mode.
- Added optional `Thresholds + events` mode so dense event markers stay available without overwhelming charts.
- Split alert overlay counts into clearer threshold/event-marker metadata.
- Removed redundant Metric dropdown and `Selected: Value` pill for single-series indicator detail charts.
- Disabled ECharts dirty-rect canvas rendering to avoid hover trails or temporary line disappearance while dragging over dense chart lines.
